buttons.button.accessible_link.help_text.message: Accessible link. Inform when a link opens a new window.

buttons.button.accessible_link_label.hel.message: If the link title is added at the end of repeated blocks of text, for example “Read more” links at the end of short teasers for blog posts, then you can provide more descriptive link text specifically for screen reader users using Accessible link label. It will be visually hidden for a normal view.

language_switcher.dropdown.display_mode..message: The language of the text in the language switcher. PageLang means the names of languages will display in the language of the page the switcher is on. Localized means the name of each language will display in that language. Hybrid is a combination of the two.
